VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://your-deployment.convex.cloud
# App URL for OAuth redirects / magic links (set on the Convex deployment).
# JWT issuer is CONVEX_SITE_URL (usually auto-set by Convex); convex/auth.config.ts
# uses that for `domain` so tokens validate — do not point `domain` at localhost unless
# that is actually your deployment issuer.
SITE_URL=http://localhost:5173
#
# Editors: sign up / sign in via the site footer, then Convex dashboard → Data → users
# → your document → set isAdmin = true.
#
# After deleting users in Data → users, clean orphaned auth rows:
#   npx convex run internal.userCleanup.sweepOrphanedAuth '{}'
